<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto my-24 sm:my-32">
  <div class="pb-5 px-4 w-full">
    <h2 class="text-3xl tracking-tight text-typography font-heading text-center lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl">
      <%= t(".reviews_header") %>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-typography text-light text-center leading-8 md:text-base md:mt-5 lg:leading-10">
      <%= tag.span(t(".reviews_subtitle_1"), class: "block") %>
      <%= tag.span(t(".reviews_subtitle_2"), class: "block") %>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-12 items-center px-2 mt-20 md:px-8 lg:items-stretch lg:flex-row lg:space-y-0 lg:space-x-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
      <div class="flex-grow border-2 p-12 border-green">
        <div class="flex">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <span>
              <%= inline_svg_tag "icons/solid/star.svg", class: "text-teal h-6 w-6", aria_hidden: true %>
            </span>
          <% end %>
          <span class="sr-only">5 star rating</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 mx-1 text-sm text-typography leading-relaxed font-light">
          Switching jobs and overcoming the period between contracts was extremely painful. <span class="font-bold">railsdevs.com is precisely what I needed</span>. Now companies come to me instead of me chasing the work. I am incredibly grateful Joe did such a favor to the Rails community and built this platform.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex flex-col justify-center mt-4 pl-[184px] h-16 w-full bg-teal-lightest">
        <div class="absolute left-12 -bottom-2 h-28 w-28 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg">
          <%# Image placeholder %>
        </div>
        <dl>
          <dt class="text-sm text-typography font-bold">
            Dusan
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-sm text-typography">
            Freelancer
          </dd>
        </dl>
